WEBVTT


00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.080
This is what I got to save my sanity.

00:00:04.081 --> 00:00:06.321
There's actually six of us that live in my house

00:00:06.322 --> 00:00:08.401
that have to use this bathroom.

00:00:08.402 --> 00:00:11.441
This is all the space we have. Just, like,

00:00:11.442 --> 00:00:13.121
so much stuff we keep in this

00:00:13.122 --> 00:00:15.241
that we kind of want accessible all the time,

00:00:15.242 --> 00:00:16.921
but we didn't want the counter all clogged up.

00:00:16.922 --> 00:00:20.441
And so this thing has been a lifesaver.

00:00:20.442 --> 00:00:23.501
And my kids keep saying that our bathroom feels like a hotel bathroom.

00:00:23.880 --> 00:00:26.640
So I love it. I love it,

00:00:26.641 --> 00:00:27.954
I love it. Super worth it.
